<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">شِعْرًا:</span> ... مَثِّلْ وُقُوفَكَ أَيُّهَا الْمَغْرُورُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ وَالسَّمَاءُ تَمُورُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَاذَا تَقُولُ إِذَا وَقَفْتَ بِمَوْقِفٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَرْدًا وَجَاءَكَ مُنْكَرٌ وَنَكِيرُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَاذَا تَقُولُ إِذَا وَقَفْتَ بِمَوْقِفٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَرْدًا ذَلِيلاً وَالْحِسَابُ عَسِيرُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَتَعَلَّقَتْ فِيكَ الْخُصُومُ وَأَنْتَ فِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَوْمِ الْحِسَابِ مُسَلْسَلٌ مَجْرُورُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَتَفَرَّقَتْ عَنْكَ الْجُنُودُ وَأَنْتَ فِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ضِيقِ الْقُبُورِ مُوَسَّدٌ مَقْبُورُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَوَدِدْتَ أَنَّكَ مَا وَلِيتَ وَلايَةً<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يَوْمًا وَلا قَالَ الأَنَامُ أَمِيرُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَبَقِيتَ بَعْدَ الْعِزِّ رَهْنَ حَفِيرَةٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فِي عَالَمِ الْمَوْتَى وَأَنْتَ حَقِيرُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَحُشِرْتَ عَرْيَانًا حَزِينًا بَاكِيًا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>قَلِقًا وَمَا لَكَ فِي الأَنَامِ مُجِيرُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَرَضِيتَ أَنْ تَحْيَا وَقَلْبَكَ دَارِسٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>عَافِي الْخَرَابَ وَجِسْمُكَ الْمَعْمُورُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَرَضِيتَ أَنْ يُحْظَى سِوَاكَ بِقُرْبِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَبَدًا وَأَنْتَ مُعَذَّبٌ مَهْجُورُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مَهِّدْ لِنَفْسِكَ حُجَّةً تَنْجُو بِهَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>يَوْمَ الْمِعَادِ وَيَوْمَ تَبْدُو الْعُورُ ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>